uru recently launched “disney infinity” and is based in san francisco “following three years of consistent operating improvement at disney interactive and a great partnership between john and jimmy we are now in a position to fulfill our original objective to consolidate our interactive business under one los angelesbased leader” said robert a iger chairman and ceo the walt disney co “with jimmy and john’s input we have created an interactive organization that is best structured to meet the demands of the fastmoving technology industry” iger added “i thank john for his many contributions to disney interactive including building tentpole products like ‘disney infinity’ and establishing the company as a leading mobile games publisher and appreciate his passion for bringing disney experiences to guests on new platforms” reorg is meant to enable disney to take better advantage of merging web and mobile entertainment platforms the company said and embrace a single strategy to generate revenue from its franchises having two presidents simply proved too complicated for disney interactive especially with leaders who wanted more resources for areas they were interested in building at the company pleasants and pitaro had been copresidents of the group since october  pleasants landed the position after disney acquired his social gaming company playdom for  million in july  playdom however hasn’t proved as lucrative of a purchase as disney had hoped with mobile games proving a more successful area for disney under pleasants disney did recently score with the launch of new game “disney infinity” which competes with activision’s hit “skylanders” franchise it also oversees popular kids destination club penguin and is behind mobile hits “where’s my water” and the more recent spinoff “where’s my mickey” see also ‘disney infinity’ reaches  million global sales milestone in a statement pitaro said pleasants “has been critical in helping disney interactive build a great foundation off of which we will continue to deliver quality interactive games mobile and web experiences that entertain and engage our guests” “i am extremely proud of the work our teams have done to create leading interactive games and experiences for our guests” pleasants said in a statement the former chief operating officer at electronic arts and ceo of ticketmaster added “through quality and innovation the business is generating tangible results and momentum and i am confident that consolidating our collective efforts at this time will lead to even greater acceleration” disney interactive showed a positive sign of growth during disney’s fourth quarter which wrapped sept  when it reported sales of  million and profits of  million a positive sign for a division that has long struggled to turn a profit the group was losing  million a year when pleasants and pitaro took over in  in fiscal  it reduced that to a loss of  million see also can disney infinity turn around the mouse houses worst performing division filed under disneydisney infinitydisney interactivejohn pleasants want to read more articles like this one subscribe to variety today post a comment  music linkin park singer died by hanging coroner confirms film steven spielberg iron giant is major part of ‘ready player one’ tv netflix unveils new ‘stranger things’ trailer at comiccon film ‘justice league’ trailer shows off dc comics big bad steppenwolf christopher nolan’s ‘dunkirk’ is the first slamdunk oscar contender of  ‘the handmaid’s tale’ scores hulu its first big emmy nominations  emmys costar faceoffs create a ‘feud’ across multiple categories emmys no ‘game of thrones’ means new drama champs will be crowned variety jobs creative development coordinator triptyk studios new york new york accountproject coordinator ad agency petrol advertising burbank california media specialist bridgewater associates westport connecticut executive director aspen film company confidential aspen colorado associate director youtuber  g