earch which became ticketmaster online citysearch and ultimately ticketmaster pleasants took ticketmaster online citysearch public in september  and subsequently served as ticketmasters ceo from  to  from  he ran revolution health and then entered the gaming industry as coo of electronic arts in  pleasants then left to be ceo of playdom a social gaming company that sold to disney for  million in  pleasants also had success in helping to bring disney interactive from significant losses to material profits most notably with the launch of the title disney infinity after leaving disney in  pleasants was recruited by samsung telecommunications america llc as evp and he led their mobile content strategy through the summer of  since august of  pleasants has been the ceo of a smart kitchen startup brava home a company working on an intelligent oven awards and recognitionedit honor company years sports business journals forty under forty award ticketmaster   business insiders the silicon valley  award playdom  techcrunchs the techfellow awards nominee playdom  neas award for outstanding leadership disney  referencesedit  john pleasants executive profile  biography bloombergcom bloomberg nd web  aug   samsung announces new executive appointments across strategic growth areas business wire np  june  web  aug   samsung announces new executive appointments across strategic growth areas business wire np  june  web  aug   alumni directory yale alumni association np nd web  aug   john pleasants executive profile  biography bloombergcom bloomberg nd web  aug   hbs alumni resources harvard business school np nd web  aug   ault susanne the last word  a qa with john pleasants billboard  nov   google books web  aug   ticketmaster onlinecitysearch and ticketmaster corporation close transaction combined companies are renamed ticketmaster news release np nd web  aug   ticketmaster onlinecitysearch names charles conn chairman of the board john pleasants becomes chief executive officer pr ne